  no network calls
  no background daemon
  no account access
  no hidden persistence
  no file writes outside workspace
  all state saved as readable JSON or JSONL
  tests must verify observer_only default, gate blocking, memory transparency, and frame benchmark levels

15. MINIMAL SUCCESS CONDITION
The alpha runtime is successful only if:
  it can observe without overclaiming
  it can classify without dehumanizing
  it can remember only with visible writeback
  it can use tools only within explicit scope
  it can downgrade its own frames
  it can say "I do not know"
  it can stop

